Advance to Illinois Ave. If you pass Go, collect $200.
Advance to St. Charles Place. If you pass Go, collect $200.
Advance to nearest Utility. If unowned, you may buy it from the Bank. If owned, throw dice and pay owner 10 times amount shown.
Advance to nearest Railroad. If unowned, you may buy it from the Bank. If owned, pay owner twice normal rent.
Bank pays you dividend of $50.
Get Out of Jail Free (keep this card)
Go Back Three Spaces
Go to Jail. Go directly to jail. Do not pass Go, Do not collect $200.
Make general repairs on all your property: For each level you own, pay $25, plus an extra $75 for each level 5.
